Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九尾查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照路頂呱呱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.39,0:00:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說會喪命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有兩面性
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.80,0:00:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然鳴人能使用九尾查克拉模式了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.57,0:00:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但並不代表他和九尾搞好了關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.79,0:00:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人的查克拉仍然會被九尾吸走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.13,0:00:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦查克拉清零 鳴人就會死…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人此刻很興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止激情太過分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.67,0:00:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用九尾查克拉當手電筒確實不錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.23,0:00:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跟丟了 跟緊了 蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.82,0:01:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.03,0:01:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是毫不客氣地消費我的查克拉啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.33,0:01:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在你體內看著你的一舉一動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是那麼天真
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.22,0:01:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰爭就讓我來終結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.48,0:01:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨也好 痛苦也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.38,0:01:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部由我來承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了我的查克拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.24,0:01:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨瘦如柴的你變回原樣一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.96,0:01:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…還真是少見啊 九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然會主動跟我搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你耐不住寂寞想找人傾訴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我現在正忙著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.17,0:02:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後再聽你說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.68,0:02:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的認為僅憑一己之力就能結束戰爭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.77,0:02:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那肯定是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.28,0:02:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你多少也感覺到敵人的規模有多龐大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.27,0:02:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且斑也在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他會設下什麼圈套哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我就將力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.59,0:02:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再吃你那套了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你變機靈了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…你早就露出馬腳了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話戰爭結束後再說 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果同伴被殺害了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仇恨隨之便會誕生…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能在事態演變成那樣之前消滅所有敵人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒敵人就會被他們憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想自己背負一切嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別總是小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別總是小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真能消除大家的仇恨並背負一切嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該出現了很多戰死者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時也孕育出了仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經在你身邊的佐助就是為仇恨所困
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對他不是毫無辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那天起 你就應該察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會跟誰對戰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗帽子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風帽墨鏡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太想和朋友打架
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是那麼回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是傳統的忍者對練
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷代的火影們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是通過忍者對練以提升實力的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出界了 就算我輸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換後面的繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是訓練還是別的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是為了分個勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就趕緊決定輸贏好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那麼麻煩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙真沒志氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一輩子也當不上中忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那可不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問為何的話 一生很漫長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期間會有很多…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鑽牛角尖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 鹿丸那傢伙才是最麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丁次也毫無鬥志
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井野 你認識他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧 父母的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿丸 丁次 結和解之印
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給忘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.78,0:08:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不擅長這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完成和解之印了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 漩渦鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.37,0:08:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸媽媽不讓我跟他說話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:09:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想和他交手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是 宇智波佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆都給我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和佐助結和解之印啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把對手打得落花流水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙怎麼回事 就會裝酷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…打敗這個受歡迎的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.99,0:09:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能備受矚目了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 我絕對不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油…鳴人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,0:09:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就是漩渦鳴人對宇智波佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有本事就來吧 拖後腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在對決前用慣用手和對方結下對立之印
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是禮儀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事隨便啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊讓我放倒這傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起 我就要人氣爆棚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如你所願立刻讓你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:09:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你們 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者對練是一直恪守的傳統訓練方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有些形式化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但忍者學校必須從基礎教起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在對決之前 一定要單手結印 面向對方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是雙手結印發動忍術動作的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表示即將進入戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.73,0:10:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是對立之印
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在對決結束 分出勝負之後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙方伸出對立之印
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互鉤在一起 結成和解之印
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從而表達出依然是夥伴的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止就是忍者對練的儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有在聽嗎 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說第二遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“好”只要說一次就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.58,0:11:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉他 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害 好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家平時看我的眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…比那更強烈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…他沒在看我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙方結下和解之印
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換下一組
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.64,0:11:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就當我不存在嗎 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 是狗屎 狗屎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬邦邦稀稀一大坨的混蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙連罵人都不會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是便秘還是拉肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望他分清楚些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.77,0:12:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問為何的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說別鑽牛角尖了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒說兩句啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗屎 硬邦邦稀稀一大坨的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說忍者對練是神聖的傳統了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊給我結和解之印
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想打嗎 拖後腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個 適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.81,0:12:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真差勁 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後呢…佐助變成什麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你將他的仇恨消除了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.54,0:13:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有 與此相反
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該清醒點了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既沒有父母 也沒有兄弟的你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能理解我什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就孤身一人的你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底能理解我什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在無論你說什麼 我都不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會將你和村裏的所有人都殺得一乾二淨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的只有那條路可以走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終你的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要麼殺了我成為守護村子的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要麼被我幹掉 成為一條喪家之犬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的仇恨反而越來越強烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身邊最親近的同伴都這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 不管是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都無法消除仇恨 也無法承擔仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…說完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我就該懼怕退縮 無動於衷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣不就如你所願了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真的是你才對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你連一個佐助都救不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還如此狂妄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.93,0:15:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如果連自己的決定都不相信 那就真完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會設法幫助佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設法解決這場戰爭的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想封印我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是那種小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.14,0:16:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你寄住在我的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就給點租金 借些查克拉給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超大玉…螺旋多連丸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來最後一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股力量是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.19,0:17:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…這是九尾的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…惹毛我了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這麼大的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然很厲害啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是六道的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我記住了 鳴人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當年的小鬼變得相當能說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九尾…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望有一天也能把你的憎恨給消除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你讓我痛苦不堪…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道被憎恨支配的滋味不好受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是九尾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒淪落到被你這臭小鬼拯救的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:18:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是憎恨的集合體
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這反而更有拯救的價值了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.30,0:19:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九尾 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我的確太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就像老爸老媽曾在我體內一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一直與我相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.24,0:19:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的想法和成長你都能瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你也許不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你一直都在注視著我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.77,0:19:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…你就繼續留在那裏關注我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助…你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:20:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許你的眼中從未有過我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我…一直都在關注著你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 佐助也好 戰爭也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光芒四射的鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.28,0:20:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月下嚴峻的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加輕鬆地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又和九尾吵架了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾獸模式是和九尾進行的查克拉拔河比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有查克拉 生命就落幕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以別亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道自己有點亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一向言出必行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的忍道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.04,0:22:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,好像有醫療忍者被暗殺了 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.29,0:22:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,寧次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,沒時間垂頭喪氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.41,0:22:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,還不知道敵人藏在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.76,0:22:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,下集火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.78,0:22:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,被狙擊的醫療忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.44,0:23:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人感受到了父母的家庭之愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.64,0:23:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者之路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.66,0:23:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火影忍者劇場版
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.98,0:23:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全國火熱上映中
